## Phase 8 – Microsoft 365 Login (Azure AD / Entra ID)

- [ ] **Azure App-Registrierung** – Multi-Tenant-App in Azure Entra ID anlegen (Client-ID + Client-Secret), Redirect-URI konfigurieren
